Package it.polimi.ingsw.listeners

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildListener
    BuildListener class is a WorkerListener used for notifying the client after a build action.
    DoubleMoveListener
    Class DoubleMoveListener is a WorkerListener used for notifying the client after a double move action.
    MoveListener
    MoveListener class is a WorkerListener used for notifying the client after a move action.
    RemoveBlockListener
    Class RemoveBlockListener is a WorkerListener used for notifying the client after a REMOVELEVEL action.
    SelectSpacesListener
    SelectSpacesListener class is a WorkerListener used for notifying client with selectable spaces.
    WinListener
    WinListener is a WorkerListener used for notifying the client with a WinMessage.
    WorkerListener
    WorkerListener class defines an interface used to communicate to View from Model.
